{"tid":2324064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube幫手like下就有錢賺？有冇咁筍？","createTime":"2020-12-13T16:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T16:15:14.000Z","uid":255859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"babacb7a8982f7d7529cda507c54c7c12737bc38","tid":2324064,"uid":255859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"最近喺Facebook ig見到有人share話係youtube幫手讚下片就有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到有朋友做緊，話1個like就有$1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁好賺 搞到我心思思 就問吓佢大概流程<br />\n話係開個帳號 之後佢會有任務俾你做 做完就即刻有錢入你個帳號 可以㩒提現去自己銀行<br />\n申請個帳會要你銀行號碼 唔係信用卡嗰啲係儲蓄<br />\n不過我不斷提醒個朋友要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知道係唔係伏 或者做緊<br />\n好似係最近突然之間幾多人share<br />\n如果唔係呃錢嘅都幾筍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知大家有咩見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: 覺得好撚伏，唔係好夠膽試"},{"pid":"395b8c69ab62e755e0b66907f78e05a1cb4f82e0","tid":2324064,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"咁我時薪咪幾錢蚊<br />\n前提佢有咁多片俾你like"},{"pid":"282a7a23fbeb74d012b308f66e50eaf1db9cebb8","tid":2324064,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395b8c69ab62e755e0b66907f78e05a1cb4f82e0","tid":2324064,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"咁我時薪咪幾錢蚊<br />\n前提佢有咁多片俾你like"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"咁我時薪咪幾<span class=\"red\">千</span>蚊<br />\n前提佢有咁多片俾你like"},{"pid":"b8379298599e191134e3467cf09af7f50a1361b4","tid":2324064,"uid":255859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395b8c69ab62e755e0b66907f78e05a1cb4f82e0","tid":2324064,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dis